role_description: An Ansible role that installs FileZilla on nearly any platform
role_description_full_overview: [FileZilla](https://filezilla-project.org/) is a free software, cross-platform FTP application, consisting of FileZilla Client and FileZilla Server. Client binaries are available for Windows, Linux, and macOS, server binaries are available for Windows only.
role_description_alt: This repository is the home of an Ansible role that installs FileZilla on nearly any platform.
